---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer
    class="relative mt-20 border-t border-white/5 bg-black/40 backdrop-blur-md overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        <div
            class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-8 mb-10"
        >
            <div class="max-w-xl">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <div
                        class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center p-1 overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/logo.png"
                            alt="Tech Hub Icon"
                            class="w-full h-full object-contain"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <span
                        class="text-xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white uppercase"
                    >
                        Tools-Tech <span class="text-blue-500">Hub</span>
                    </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed italic">
                    Un espacio dedicado a compartir conocimientos, experiencias
                    técnicas y soluciones a fallas comunes. Herramientas y guías
                    creadas por técnicos para técnicos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <a
                    href="https://zymtaxis.com"
                    target="_blank"
                    class="flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-2.5 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl transition-all group"
                >
                    <img
                        src="/original-mini.ico"
                        alt="Zymtaxis Icon"
                        class="w-5 h-5 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                    />
                    <span
                        class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                        >zymtaxis.com</span
                    >
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Barra Inferior Discreta -->
        <div
            class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4"
        >
            <p
                class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]"
            >
                &copy; {currentYear} Zymtaxis Tech Solutions. Todos los derechos reservados.
            </p>

            <div
                class="flex items-center gap-4 text-[9px] font-bold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest"
            >
                <span>By DanijDev</span>
                <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full"></span>
                <span>Venezuela 🇻🇪</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
